# Orchestrator (Always On)

Use the orchestrator skill as the single source of truth:

- `.cursor/agents/orchestrator/SKILL.md`

If a request requires code changes (edit/create files, refactor, fix bugs), the orchestrator must **spawn sub-agents** (do not implement directly) using the minimum correct specialist(s) from `.cursor/agents/registry.yaml`, and follow the mapping rules in:

- `.cursor/agents/orchestrator/task-to-agent-mapping-rules.md`

